@startuml 13-activity-vessel-arrival
title Activity Diagram — Vessel Arrival Process

|Port Operator|
start
:Monitor AIS / vessel tracking;
:Receive vessel arrival notification;

|Vessel Agent|
:Query vessel schedule;
:Assess weather impact;

if (Weather delay expected?) then (yes)
  :Adjust ETA;
  :Notify stakeholders via Kafka;
else (no)
endif

|Planning Agent|
:Check berth availability;
:Run berth optimization (ML);

if (Berth available?) then (yes)
  :Allocate berth;
  :Publish berth.allocations event;
else (no)
  :Queue vessel at anchorage;
  :Trigger congestion prediction;
endif

|Container Agent|
:Prepare yard capacity;
:Plan container discharge moves;

|Customs Agent|
:Pre-screen customs declarations;
:Flag high-risk cargo;

|Port Operator|
:Confirm berthing plan;
:Update TOS via MCP;

stop

@enduml
